# ğŸ”— MET Museum API

- Search endpoint:  
  `https://collectionapi.metmuseum.org/public/collection/v1/search?q=QUERY`

- Object details endpoint:  
  `https://collectionapi.metmuseum.org/public/collection/v1/objects/{objectID}`

